  "body": "<p>For this month's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/front-row-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Main Kit</a> only layout at <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/new?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a>, I tried to push myself to try new techniques with common supplies.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/09ab4a8e8cad2821.jpg?v=1782536188\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I started out by stitching three arrows with white embroidery floss.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b173e43b0a99a9b3.jpg?v=1782536190\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Next, I added a few droplets of Calico White Mister Huey.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cad68309eaf8aaaa.jpg?v=1782536194\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5b8d82a1d625414d.jpg?v=1782536196\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>From there, I arranged my photo, patterned paper, and embellishments to my liking and secured them down.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a54e49e08b7b5a72.jpg?v=1782536199\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Then I placed a strip of that awesome ombre washi tape onto a scrap piece of white cardstock and cut out a couple of hearts to place around my page.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/58f59e433d3bbdbb.jpg?v=1782536202\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0df05574105ec65d.jpg?v=1782536204\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>After the hearts were glued down (using a mix of dimensional adhesive and a tape runner), I cut out a row of arrows from the SC patterned paper and placed it on the page.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/017ed1ce105e7470.jpg?v=1782536207\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Using the American Crafts' cardstock letter stickers, I spelled out my title and determined it was done!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/36dbcd28c6bbcb39.jpg?v=1782536210\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9bc4ff59bde11606.jpg?v=1782536212\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>You can see more of my layouts from this month's kit <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/front-row/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">right here</a>!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}